Implementors

In yet_another_parachain_runtime::polkadot_sdk_frame::testing_prelude

yet_another_parachain_runtime::polkadot_sdk_frame::testing_prelude

Trait DecodeWithMemTracking

pub trait DecodeWithMemTracking: Decode { }
Expand description

Marker trait used for identifying types that call the [Input::on_before_alloc_mem] hook while decoding.

Dyn Compatibility§

This trait is not dyn compatible.

In older versions of Rust, dyn compatibility was called "object safety", so this trait is not object safe.
